riel Sharon">Sharon</a> (2004-06)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Roni_Bar-On" title="Roni Bar-On">Bar-On</a> (2006-07)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Meir_Sheetrit" title="Meir Sheetrit">Sheetrit</a> (2007-)</span></div>
